<p>I want to write more <a href="https://taonaw.com/2025/04/02/correction-about-journelly.html">about Journelly</a>, but the problem is that it&rsquo;s too effective at what it does. Creating notes with it is so easy and streamlined that it&rsquo;s starting to change my entire workflow for project notes, and that&rsquo;s a pretty big change.</p>
